<span id="freeTextContainer4337116167351730547">I have very few books that I have rated 5 stars. A 5 is reserved for the best of the best for me. Books that I look forward to carving out time to read, books that I think about when I&apos;m not reading them. <br/>My review won&apos;t do this fine little book justice. The writing was amazing, the story was engaging, the characters were real, there was emotion - joy, sadness, heartbreak, wonder, hatred, AND there is a sequel. <br/>Maybe this is why I rate it so highly? I can&apos;t wait to curl up with these characters </span>
  <span id="freeText4337116167351730547" style="display:none">I have very few books that I have rated 5 stars. A 5 is reserved for the best of the best for me. Books that I look forward to carving out time to read, books that I think about when I'm not reading them. <br />My review won't do this fine little book justice. The writing was amazing, the story was engaging, the characters were real, there was emotion - joy, sadness, heartbreak, wonder, hatred, AND there is a sequel. <br />Maybe this is why I rate it so highly? I can't wait to curl up with these characters again in the next book that promises to pick up where this one left off. <br />This book reminded me of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1103.Snow_Flower_and_the_Secret_Fan" title="Snow Flower and the Secret Fan by Lisa See" rel="nofollow noopener">Snow Flower and the Secret Fan</a> by Lisa See, so if you liked that book you will love this one.</span>
