<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/141462.The_Feast_of_Roses"><img alt="The Feast of Roses (Taj Mahal Trilogy, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442816122l/141462._SX98_.jpg" />
